1
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:16,410
Brother,

2
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:22,790
this poison was never meant to kill you.

3
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,370
But unfortunately, you brought this upon yourself for Lin Mingxuan.

4
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:28,950
What have you done to Mingxuan?

5
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,000
Don't worry.

6
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,410
She's safe for now.

7
00:01:33,790 --> 00:01:35,250
As long as you confess,

8
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,450
and abdicate the position of city lord,

9
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,660
I'll let you see her.

10
00:01:50,450 --> 00:01:52,160
You want to be the city lord.

11
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:58,330
But there are plenty in the court who won't agree.

12
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,450
So you want me to admit to patricide,

13
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:05,410
so you can take the position rightfully.

14
00:02:07,410 --> 00:02:09,080
And become the city lord.

15
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:13,500
Xiao Jingyu gave up everything for that woman.

16
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:16,410
He abandoned years of influence in the court.

17
00:02:17,410 --> 00:02:18,250
And you,

18
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:22,660
carry the crime of regicide and usurpation.

19
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:27,200
Tell me, besides me,

20
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:30,040
who else is fit to be city lord?

21
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,450
Don't even think about it.

22
00:02:38,370 --> 00:02:40,000
I won't let you succeed.

23
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,950
Guards!

24
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,160
Torture him.

25
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:46,370
Keep going until he confesses.

26
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,950
Young madam.

27
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,200
You are Grand Tutor Zhang.

28
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,830
Yes, I am.

29
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:13,790
Why are Lord Zhang and all the other officials here?

30
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:14,950
Where is Jingyang?

31
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:18,120
Princess Pingning has announced to the world

32
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:22,000
that the young lord plotted a coup and killed the city lord.

33
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:26,500
Anyone in court who dares to question this matter

34
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,160
will be locked up here.

35
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,040
That's impossible.

36
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:31,250
I was with him the whole day.

37
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,700
We never saw the city lord.

38
00:03:34,370 --> 00:03:35,160
Besides,

39
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:38,000
there was a strange scent in that room.

40
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,040
After that, Jingyang

41
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,950
was poisoned because of it.

42
00:03:41,950 --> 00:03:45,000
During this period, Princess Pingning

43
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:48,790
used the city lord's illness as an excuse

44
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,410
to take control of the court.

45
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,790
I'm afraid that from that moment on,

46
00:03:52,950 --> 00:03:55,580
the princess was already planning for today.

47
00:03:56,450 --> 00:03:59,370
Then... doesn't that mean Jingyang is in danger?

48
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:02,200
It seems just as Lord Liu said,

49
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:04,250
things are about to change.

50
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,750
What are you trying to do?

51
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,080
Where is the young city lord?

52
00:04:16,330 --> 00:04:17,160
Come out!

53
00:04:31,450 --> 00:04:33,660
Zhulan, so it really was you.

54
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,660
So what if you recognized me?

55
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:41,580
Today,

56
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,290
all of you must die.

57
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:56,200
Jingyang! Jingyang!

58
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,790
Mingxuan, are you alright?

59
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:07,500
I'm fine.

60
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:09,330
Good, as long as you're okay.

61
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:10,790
Why did you stop?

62
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:12,450
Keep going.

63
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:13,330
Wait a moment.

64
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:17,450
Hurry, go! Go!

65
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,950
No, I won't.

66
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,410
Go! I won't leave.

67
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,620
Xiao Jingyang.

68
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,620
If you confess your crimes and abdicate,

69
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,540
I can let one of you keep your body intact.

70
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,660
If you don't confess,

71
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:32,410
then don't blame me for forgetting our brotherhood.

72
00:05:32,410 --> 00:05:33,790
This has nothing to do with her.

73
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,910
Let her go.

74
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:39,540
Go!

75
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,910
Stop! Stop!

76
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:43,580
Don't hit him! Stop!

77
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,080
Xiao Jingyang, think carefully.

78
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,910
Alright.

79
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:52,450
I promise you. I promise.

80
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:55,290
You should have agreed earlier.

81
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,330
Guards!

82
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:58,000
Here!

83
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,540
Zhulan

84
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:33,910
I'll leave this to you.

85
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,290
I, the Princess,

86
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,120
I,

87
00:06:39,790 --> 00:06:42,620
need to prepare for tomorrow's succession ceremony.

88
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:45,330
Yes.

89
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,620
Why are you so foolish?

90
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:50,750
All of you, leave.

91
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,410
Yes.

92
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:10,790
I'm fine.

93
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:12,330
Second Young Master saved me.

94
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:22,790
Don't move.

95
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:25,330
Young Master.

96
00:07:25,330 --> 00:07:26,500
Don't call me Young Master.

97
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,870
I won't keep a dog that bites its master.

98
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,410
I really don't understand.

99
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:34,370
What exactly did Xiao Wenxi give you

100
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,500
that made you betray me for her?

101
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:38,660
My life was given to me by the Princess.

102
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:40,950
Your kindness,

103
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:43,160
I can only repay in the next life.

104
00:07:43,580 --> 00:07:44,910
You aid the wicked.

105
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:47,500
Your hands are stained with so many lives.

106
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,250
And you still want a next life?

107
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:56,830
This sword strike is to repay you on Qiangqiang's behalf.

108
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,080
This is wound medicine.

109
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,870
You can make do with it for now.

110
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:05,290
I'll stand guard outside for you.

111
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:12,660
Second Brother.

112
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,660
Thank you.

113
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:19,080
No need to thank me between brothers.

114
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,200
Quick, let me see your wound.

115
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:29,750
Mingxuan.

116
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:31,870
I'm fine.

117
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,330
Let me apply the medicine first.

118
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:35,330
How could you possibly be fine?

119
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:37,120
You're so badly hurt.

120
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,370
Let me apply the medicine first.

121
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:39,580
Then I'll treat the wound.

122
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,040
Be good.

123
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,040
The Second Young Master said

124
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,870
he wants to turn their scheme against them.

125
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,040
He plans to stay undercover by Xiao Wenxi's side.

126
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:06,500
But there's something

127
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:07,950
I've always found strange.

128
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,950
How did he manage to escape?

129
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,500
And how can he move so freely

130
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:14,830
in the City Lord's manor?

131
00:09:20,410 --> 00:09:21,450
Does it not hurt enough?

132
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,580
You still have the energy to worry about this?

133
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:27,200
I'm just concerned, that's all.

134
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,950
You always respect Princess Pingning so much,

135
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,500
but she treats you like this.

136
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,290
If they join forces again in the future,

137
00:09:35,290 --> 00:09:35,540
then...

138
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,290
No.

139
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,410
That won't happen.

140
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:42,370
You'll understand this matter in time.

141
00:09:43,950 --> 00:09:45,500
For now, let me get you out of here first.

142
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:46,950
What about you?

143
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:52,080
My father can't have died in vain.

144
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:54,700
And I can't ignore

145
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:56,040
the officials who are still imprisoned.

146
00:09:57,450 --> 00:09:58,700
Then I want to stay.

147
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:00,040
Xiao Jingyang,

148
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:01,950
you can't leave me behind.

149
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:07,160
Sorry.

150
00:10:07,370 --> 00:10:08,790
I touched your wound.

151
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:09,870
Does it hurt?

152
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:10,870
It's fine, it doesn't hurt.

153
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:13,450
Not at all.

154
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,290
It's very dangerous here.

155
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,330
If you stay,

156
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,660
I'll be worried.

157
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,120
Xiao Jingyang,

158
00:10:46,250 --> 00:10:48,000
we've missed out on too much already.

159
00:10:50,410 --> 00:10:51,790
From now on, every day

160
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:54,750
I don't want to miss you anymore.

161
00:10:58,160 --> 00:11:00,950
Whether in life or death,

162
00:11:01,950 --> 00:11:03,620
I want to be with you.

163
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:09,450
Alright.

164
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:13,250
In this lifetime,

165
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:17,290
we'll face it together.
